{"tid":1928578,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★滯英留學生趕死線前衝港　機票炒至近7萬元天價","createTime":"2020-03-16T13:00:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T13:02:20.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0a985a1c451c4a0443c9f7b0b7a0c660d31cecce","tid":1928578,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T13:00:27.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎疫情在歐洲多國有失控迹象，港府亦收緊對來自包括英國、法國及意大利等近30個歐洲國家人士的入境限制，例如周四(19日)凌晨零時起，要求由英國、美國及愛爾蘭抵港的人士，必須接受14天強制家居檢疫。為了逃避疫情及坐「疫監」，大批滯留在英國的港人留學生瘋搶回港機票，務求在周四之前衝港，致使直航機票被炒到近7萬港元的「天價」。有旅行社更稱，返港機票現時「一票難求」，即使有錢都未必買到。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200316/bkn-20200316171922039-0316_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200316%2Fbkn-20200316171922039-0316_00822_001.html&d=eokTwrWYlXUgHXHl4H%2BebQVsaiM9baN%2FEtUhsAXiQ7E%3D&h=03d2e1c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200316/bkn-20200316171922039-0316_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"eb8def9ac1335834a2fa9cfc027d6c49b9c606ff","tid":1928578,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T13:00:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdb2f46d4a4ee192f61c6892b88f1cd4fa582d43","tid":1928578,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T13:01:05.000Z","msg":"全數驗肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab7b93acae906c5e75bb69ea956b4b89060fa515","tid":1928578,"uid":53037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T13:02:20.000Z","msg":"遲早開返關比支那人落香港<br />\n